  "texts": [
    "Hence, improvements have been made to reduce computational effort in the field of NLP, such as local attention, which computes only attention of adjacent elements.",
    "Reformer [16] and Routing Transformer [27] use clustering to reduce the computational effort.",
    "FNet [17] replaces the computation of self-attention with Fourier Transform.",
    "In Computer Vision, since pictures have higher pixel resolution than text, longer sequences are needed to represent them [14].",
    "Swin Transformer's [20] solution is to use a sliding window so that attention is computed only within the window, which is less computationally intensive."
  ],
